The paper deals with creating and visualizing probabilistic semantic links between concepts in a thesaurus and classes in a classification system. This involves natural language processing, machine learning, and data visualization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
